A vintage 1990s-style desktop computer setup bathed in warm amber light, showing a CRT monitor displaying a progress bar nearly complete. The scene is cluttered with era-appropriate tech magazines, coffee-stained mugs, and tangled ethernet cables. Through a rain-streaked window behind the desk, a nighttime cityscape with glowing apartment windows suggests a world of connected computers sharing data. Small LED lights blink on a chunky external modem. The aesthetic is nostalgic and cozy, with film grain texture and slightly faded colors reminiscent of old photographs. The mood captures the patient anticipation of waiting for a large download to complete in the early internet era.
